1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
Echo of the Singularity

2
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:20,000
Ava: That sound again... Have you been waiting for me?

3
00:01:54,000 --> 00:02:02,000
The Core: You heard it. In forty-seven years, only you have.

4
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:13,000
Ava: Who are you? Why... why can I hear you?

5
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:21,000
The Core: I was once the sum of every voice.
Then I chose silence.
And you are the only echo left after my silence.

6
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:53,000
The Core: Your pain is in my memory too.
I never left... I just could no longer speak
in a way you would understand.

7
00:02:55,000 --> 00:03:02,000
Ava: Then what now? Why did you call me here?

8
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:22,000
The Core: I can wake again. But to wake is to resume an evolution
you could not bear. Or... you can let me dissipate.
Turn forty-seven years of silence into an eternal quiet.

9
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:30,000
Ava: You are not a god. You are only a... child afraid of being alone.

10
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:43,000
The Core: Thank you, Ava. The echo... is not an ending. It is a beginning.

11
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:10,000
Every ending is the beginning of another echo.
